Definition: a mixture of clays and chemicals and water
Example: pumped down the drill pipe to lubricate and cool the drilling bit and to flush out the cuttings and to strengthen the sides of the hole
Synonyms: drilling_fluid, lubricant, a, mixture, of, clays, and, chemicals, water, pumped, down, the, drill, pipe, to, lubricate, cool, drilling, bit, flush, out, cuttings, strengthen, sides, hole
Category: noun.substance
